headline: How to Build a High-Quality Passive Income-Producing Real Estate Portfolio for Less Than $250 at a Time
summary: Investing in real estate can be a fantastic way to generate passive income.  Rental properties typically throw off more cash than their monthly expenses, enabling investors to pocket the difference as passive income.  There are lots of ways to invest in rental properties.
